Yewande Lawal Simpson bụ onye na eme ihe nkiri na ihe nlere anya na Naịjirịa
A na-akpọbu ya Yewande Lawal Adebisi
Ọ meriri Miss Lagos Carnival Pageant na 2012
Wendy Lawal bụ onye Ogun State, Nigeria
A mụrụ ya na Febụwarị 21, 1991 na Ogun State
Ọ bụ nwa nke ise n'ime ụmụ isii
Agụmgu akwụkwọ praịmarị na nke sekọndrị Wendy Lawal bu na Naijiria,  o nwekwara nzere bachelọ na Nka na Mahadum Lagos
Ọrụ ime ihe nkiri Lawal bidoro n'afọ 2009 ka o gosichara n'usoro ihe onyonyo Naijiria Living in Lagos
Ọ meriri Miss Lagos Carnival Pageant na n'otu afọ ahụ, ọ nwetara ọrụ iji gosipụta dị ka Shoshanna na ihe nkiri a na-egosiputa na onyonyo bu Tinsel na 2012
ọ gosiputara na obere ihe nkiri, TV na usoro weebụ dị ka: The Men's Club, Jemeji, Journey to Self, The room, Out of Dịghị, Foreign Love, na ndị ọzọ
Wendy Lawal bụ onye mmeriri na Miss Lagos Carnival Pageant, nke emere na Eko Hotels and Suites, Lagos
